import React, { useState, useEffect } from 'react' import "./Checkout.css" import { useParams } from 'react-router-dom' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' const Checkout = () => { const [product, setProduct] = useState() const productId = useParams().productId const cartItems = useSelector(state => state.cart.items) const exist = cartItems.find(item => item.id === productId.id) if (exist) { setProduct(exist) } else { const fetchProduct = async () => { // setLoading(true) const response = await fetch(`https://fakestoreapi.com/products/${productId}`) const data = await response.json() setProduct(data) // setLoading(false) } useEffect(() => { fetchProduct() }, [productId]) } return (
